<c id="ref280" level="series"> <did> <unittitle>Subject files</unittitle> <unitid>Series VI.</unitid> <unitid type="aspace_uri">/repositories/2/archival_objects/946923</unitid> <unitdate datechar="creation" type="inclusive">1960-2017, undated</unitdate> </did> <scopecontent id="aspace_297126bec1095480b8fc84a44c312fc6"> <head>Scope and Contents</head> <p>The Subject files series (1960-2017, undated) comprises many articles, handouts, pamphlets, and publications, related to church and state issues, arranged by topic, organizational name, or title. Part of the series includes articles, newsletters, and booklets published by the Americans for Religious Liberty, an organization started by former staff member of Americans' United, Edd Doerr. Of note, the series includes a white nationalist newsletter,<title render="italic">Southern Patriot</title>, presumably collected by Charles Sumner or other Americans' United members for oppositional research.</p> </scopecontent> <c id="ref281" level="file"/> <c id="ref282" level="file"/> <c id="ref283" level="file"/> <c id="ref298" level="file"/> <c id="ref299" level="file"/> <c id="ref300" level="file"/> <c id="ref301" level="file"/> <c id="ref302" level="file"/> <c id="ref303" level="file"/> <c id="ref304" level="file"/> <c id="ref305" level="file"/> <c id="ref306" level="file"/> <c id="ref307" level="file"/> <c id="ref308" level="file"/> <c id="ref309" level="file"/> <c id="ref310" level="file"/> <c id="ref311" level="file"/> <c id="ref312" level="file"/> <c id="ref313" level="file"/> <c id="ref314" level="file"/> <c id="ref315" level="file"/> <c id="ref316" level="file"/> <c id="ref317" level="file"/> <c id="ref318" level="file"/> <c id="ref319" level="file"/> <c id="ref320" level="file"/> <c id="ref321" level="file"/> <c id="ref322" level="file"/> <c id="ref323" level="file"/> <c id="ref324" level="file"/> <c id="ref325" level="file"/> <c id="ref326" level="file"/> <c id="ref327" level="file"/> <c id="ref328" level="file"/> <c i